text: Ilikovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baymurzinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 156 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 45 km from Mishkino, 7 km from Baymurzino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Ilikovo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
